Module kivakit.core.commandline
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.commandline

Class ArgumentList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.commandline.ArgumentList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Countable, Sized, AsString, java.lang.Iterable<Argument>
    public class ArgumentList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Argument>, AsString, Sized
    A list of Arguments passed on a command line and retrieved with CommandLine.arguments() after command line parsing with CommandLineParser. Individual arguments values can be retrieved as typed values with Argument.get(ArgumentParser). If the arguments are all of the same type they can be retrieved as a list with argumentValues(ArgumentParser).
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    CommandLine, Argument
